---
import "@fontsource/roboto";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Nanas Sound">
  <div class="px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center my-10">Our story: Nanas Sound</h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-800">
        <p>
          <b>Nanas Sound</b> began in 2021 as a passionate music project by Asep Bagja, a software engineer and electronic music enthusiast, in Tallinn, Estonia. Originally, Asep started Nanas Sound to release his own music, which you can now enjoy on
          <a href="https://music.youtube.com/channel/UC8C4fWKZJvALsC_9I0M5kFg?si=G4kNmx5pyZQO4CTo" 
             class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-800" 
             target="_blank">YouTube Music</a>,
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@bepitulaz" 
             class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-800" 
             target="_blank">YouTube</a>,
          <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/3ZluC2z0z35Pdv8Aky7qMx?si=zXISVL_HRmyMgxuAoYnzeg" 
             class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-800" 
             target="_blank">Spotify</a>, and
          <a href="https://music.apple.com/ee/artist/asep-bagja/1650464458" 
             class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-800" 
             target="_blank">Apple Music</a>.
        </p>

        <p>
          Driven by a fascination with modular synthesizers, Asep expanded Nanas Sound beyond music production. He began designing and building Eurorack modules, transforming his hobby into a brand. Today, Nanas Sound proudly offers DIY Eurorack modules and 3D-printed synth parts for fellow enthusiasts and creators.
        </p>

        <p>
          For any inquiries, feel free to reach out to Asep at 
          <a href="mailto:asep@nanassound.com" 
             class="text-yellow-600 hover:text-yellow-800">asep@nanassound.com</a>. 
          Join us on this creative journey and explore the endless possibilities of sound.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold my-10">Team...it's only him for now ðŸ™‚</h3>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <img class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full" src="/img/avatar.jpg" alt="Asep Bagja" />
          <div>
            <h5 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Asep Bagja</h5>
            <p>
              Chief Everything Officer<br />
              I do everything from designing, coding, soldering, testing, and shipping.<br />
              I also do music production and release my music under my name.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
